Chinese stars attend Cinema Against AIDS event in Cannes
2013-05-24 02:30:32 GMT
Chinese actresses Zhang Ziyi and Zhang Yuqi attended amfAR’s Cinema Against AIDS event in Cannes Thursday.Hollywood stars like Jessica Chastain, Stacy Keibler, Janet Jackson, Rosie Huntington-Whiteley and Adrien Brody were also present.The gala, now in its 20th year, was held at Hotel du Cap-Eden-Roc, just east of the Cannes Film Festival site. Models, including Karlie Kloss, Alessandra Ambrosio and Huntington-Whiteley walked the runway during the event, while the legendary Dame Shirley Bassey performed on stage.  
